{"lemma":"نَفَحاتِ","slug":"نَفَحاتِ","root":"ن.ف.ح","root_slug":"ن-ف-ح","root_link":"/words/roots/ن-ف-ح","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"نَفْحَة","root":"نفح","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n40177"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%86%D9%8E%D9%81%D9%8E%D8%AD%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"instance noun of نَفْح (nafḥ)"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n40177","headword_ar":"نَفْحَةٌ","root":"nfH","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An odour,"},{"kind":"text","text":"whether good or bad: or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a plenteous odour;"},{"kind":"text","text":"differing from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nafoxapN","text_ar":"نَفْخَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is a slight odour: (AHn, in L, art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nfx","text_ar":"نفخ"},{"kind":"text","text":":) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nafaHaAtN","text_ar":"نَفَحَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (L.) You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lahu nafoHapN Tay~ibapN","text_ar":"لَهُ نَفْحَةٌ طَيِّبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, L.) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xabiyvapN","text_ar":"خَبِيثَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It has a good,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sweet,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a bad,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"foul, odour."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nafoHapN","text_ar":"نَفْحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A blast,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"breath, of wind."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nafoHapN mina AlS~abaA","text_ar":"نَفْحَةٌ مِنَ الصَّبَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A pleasant and fragrant blast of the east wind."},{"kind":"text","text":"And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nfHpN mino","text_ar":"نفحةٌ مِنْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"samuwmK","text_ar":"سَمُومٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A grievous blast of hot wind."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHeyth.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nafoHapN mina AlEa*aAbi","text_ar":"نَفْحَةٌ مِنَ العَذَابِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A part,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portion, of punishment:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a grievous blast of punishment:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHeyth:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a most violent infliction of punishment."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nafoHapN Ald~ami","text_ar":"نَفْحَةٌ الدَّمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The first gush of blood from a wound."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Khálid Ibn-Jembeh, L.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nafoHapN","text_ar":"نَفْحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A single churning"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHoDapN","text_ar":"مَحْضَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"so in the A and TA: in. the CK and a MS copy of the K."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHoDap","text_ar":"مَحْضَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"H","text_ar":"ح"},{"kind":"text","text":"unpointed:) of milk. (A, K.) ―         -b7-  [See 1.] ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nafoHpN","text_ar":"نَفْحةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A gift:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) [pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nafaHaAtN","text_ar":"نَفَحَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. ―         -b9-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lA tazaAlu lifulaAn nafaHaAtN mna AlmaEoruwfi","text_ar":"لا تَزَالُ لِفُلَان نَفَحَاتٌ منَ المَعْرُوفِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There cease not to be attributable to such a one acts of kindness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"favours."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) ―         -b10-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tEar~aDuwA","text_ar":"تعَرَّضُوا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"linafaHaAti raHomapi A@ll~`hi","text_ar":"لِنَفَحَاتِ رَحْمَةِ ا@للّٰهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  (TA:) see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ErD","text_ar":"عرض"},{"kind":"text","text":", voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taEar~aDa","text_ar":"تَعَرَّضَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["L","S","K","AHeyth","Msb","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}